ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectHog Farm Transition Program
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to establish the Hog Farm Transition Program and to provide for federal contributions to assist those hog producers who wish to exit the industry.
